- Ah. You thought about it.

121
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:43,150
Well, Yamazaki... thank you.

122
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:48,880
Thanks for your hard work.

123
00:17:02,110 --> 00:17:06,860
